data.description: Nestled within the serene confines of Deerwood Village, an exclusive gated community renowned for its tranquil ambiance, lies this stunning single-family home. Boasting 2,113 square feet of meticulously crafted living space, this residence offers the perfect fusion of modern elegance and comfort.    Upon entry, you are greeted by a spacious foyer that sets the tone for the home's welcoming atmosphere. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, providing an ideal space for both entertaining guests and everyday living. Sunlight pours in through large windows, casting a warm glow upon the stylish interiors adorned with contemporary finishes and designer accents.    The heart of the home is undoubtedly the gourmet kitchen, which features sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet storage. With a breakfast nook and a formal dining area, it is perfect for enjoying morning coffee or casual meals with family.    Adjacent to the main living area, you'll find a versatile office space, providing the ideal environment for remote work or quiet study. This flexible room can easily be transformed to suit your specific needs, whether it be a home office, guest bedroom, or hobby room.    Retreat to the private master suite, where relaxation awaits. This sanctuary boasts a spacious layout and a luxurious en-suite bathroom complete with a soaking tub, separate shower, and dual vanity sinks. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms and a second full bathroom provide comfort and convenience for family members or overnight guests.    Outside, the meticulously landscaped yard offers a serene escape, perfect for alfresco dining, gardening, or simply unwinding amidst nature's beauty. Don't miss your opportunity to experience the epitome of modern living in Deerwood Village.
